sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 로그인 회원
    participant JS as pets.jsp Ajax
    participant C as PetProfileController
    participant S as PetProfileService
    participant M as PetProfileMapper
    participant DB as Oracle

    User->>JS: 등록/수정 저장
    JS->>C: POST /mypage/pets/save
    C->>C: session memberNo 확인
    C->>S: savePet(vo, memberNo)
    alt petId null 신규
        S->>M: insertPet
        M->>DB: INSERT TB_PET
    else 수정
        S->>S: 본인 소유 검증
        S->>M: updatePet
        M->>DB: UPDATE TB_PET
    end
    C-->>JS: JSON success message
